"{    \"translations\": [        {            \"english_version\": \"The US president criticizes an Iranian counteroffer to end the war, saying the month-long ceasefire is very weak. There are calls to investigate the 16 March airstrike, which the UN says likely killed more people, as a war crime.\",            \"english_title\": \"US President Criticizes Iranian Offer\",            \"translated_version\": \"El presidente de Estados Unidos critica una oferta de Ir\u00e1n para terminar la guerra, diciendo que el alto el fuego de un mes es muy d\u00e9bil. Hay llamados para investigar el ataque a\u00e9reo del 16 de marzo, que la ONU dice que probablemente mat\u00f3 a m\u00e1s personas, como un crimen de guerra.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Presidente de EE.UU. critica oferta de Ir\u00e1n\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Yoweri Museveni, 81, won disputed elections in January to extend his 40-year rule.\",            \"english_title\": \"Yoweri Museveni Wins Disputed Elections\",            \"translated_version\": \"Yoweri Museveni, de 81 a\u00f1os, gan\u00f3 elecciones discutidas en enero para extender su gobierno de 40 a\u00f1os.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Yoweri Museveni gana elecciones discutidas\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"The head of the World Health Organization warns that the situation could still change and there might be more confirmed cases.\",            \"english_title\": \"WHO Warns of Possible Changes\",            \"translated_version\": \"El jefe de la Organizaci\u00f3n Mundial de la Salud advierte que la situaci\u00f3n a\u00fan podr\u00eda cambiar y podr\u00eda haber m\u00e1s casos confirmados.\",            \"translated_title\": \"OMS advierte de posibles cambios\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"The company behind Canvas says it has reached an agreement with the hackers who disrupted thousands of colleges and universities.\",            \"english_title\": \"Canvas Reaches Agreement with Hackers\",            \"translated_version\": \"La empresa detr\u00e1s de Canvas dice que ha llegado a un acuerdo con los hackers que interrumpieron miles de colegios y universidades.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Canvas llega a acuerdo con hackers\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"The effective closure of the Strait of Hormuz has severely disrupted global supplies of energy and petrochemicals.\",            \"english_title\": \"Strait of Hormuz Closure Disrupts Supplies\",            \"translated_version\": \"El cierre efectivo del Estrecho de Ormuz ha interrumpido gravemente los suministros globales de energ\u00eda y productos petroqu\u00edmicos.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Cierre del Estrecho de Ormuz interrumpe suministros\"        }    ]}"